    "description": "Join the Maersk India Consulting Pvt Ltd family as a Warehouse Manager in Chandigarh. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Maersk India Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nMaersk India Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chandigarh, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Maersk India Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
